Package eus.klimu.notification.domain.service.implementation

Class LocalizedNotificationServiceImp

java.lang.Object
eus.klimu.notification.domain.service.implementation.LocalizedNotificationServiceImp
All Implemented Interfaces:
LocalizedNotificationService
@Service
public class LocalizedNotificationServiceImp
extends java.lang.Object
implements LocalizedNotificationService
The implementation of the localized notification service. It interacts with the different localized notifications using a localized notification repository, modifying directly on the database.
